{"tid":684701,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［緊急］[求救] 旅行遇到gay佬室友點算","createTime":"2018-05-30T18:16:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T22:43:50.000Z","uid":96401,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"835b3c08aa1c8b91b0d4ec417aa5e983cd5f781e","tid":684701,"uid":96401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T18:16:25.000Z","msg":"交代番小小背景先，小弟係同成班朋友去英國旅行，而其中就有一個人跟埋黎啦（同我地大部分人都唔熟，只不過係叫做互相認識）<br />\n<br />\n係依到就用A黎稱呼佢啦<br />\n<br />\n起初都係諗住各有各玩啦，然後成班人一齊租屋住，點知住住下俾我地發現左啲咁既野：<br />\n<br />\n有一晚當A自稱返入房休息之後，我地成班人就係廳到吹水。隔左一陣我地諗住入A房到拎野既時候，竟然發現：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">屌你老母A係到一隻手係lin頭打圈 一隻手插屎忽窿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家好撚老尷，但係同時又驚自己菊花不保，仲有幾晚點撚算好"},{"pid":"35ecc96017cd58e2fb745a0e86df587b9faa0a0e","tid":684701,"uid":96401,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T18:19:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔好比佢沉，呢鋪好撚甘</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7e8593301819abae05d735094531de8b31d0a5c","tid":684701,"uid":96401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T18:21:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6473dde5bc2d009280eebce25db23a922f5116ef","tid":684701,"uid":142508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T18:23:43.000Z","msg":"一路順風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"856a4d0872df40133af24d1a79793a7206b7bb3c","tid":684701,"uid":96